      <h1>Welcome to Shadow OS: A New Era of Privacy</h1>
      <p class="post-date">March 26, 2025</p>
      <div class="post-content">
        <p>We’re thrilled to introduce <strong>Shadow OS</strong>, a Debian-based Linux distribution built from the ground up with privacy and security in mind. In an era where data breaches and surveillance are all too common, Shadow OS offers a sanctuary for users who value their digital freedom.</p>
        <p>What sets Shadow OS apart? Here are some key features:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Privacy by Default</strong>: Out-of-the-box settings prioritize anonymity and data protection.</li>
          <li><strong>Open Source</strong>: Fully transparent code that anyone can audit or contribute to.</li>
          <li><strong>Lightweight & Fast</strong>: Optimized to run smoothly on both modern and older hardware.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Whether you’re a tech enthusiast, a privacy advocate, or just someone looking for a reliable operating system, Shadow OS is designed for you. Download it today and join us in shaping a more secure digital future!</p>
        <p><a href="/download.html">Get Shadow OS Now</a></p>
